title: The General [Buster Keaton] (1927)
description:
The General (1927)

Written and Directed by Buster Keaton & Clyde Bruckman.

Starring Buster Keaton, Marion Mack.

Keaton&#039;s best silent feature, setting comedy against true Civil War story of stolen train, Union spies.


Recently came in at No. 18 in the American Film Institute&#039;s 100 Greatest American Films Poll.

Currently No. 27 on the "They Shoot Pictures, Don&#039;t They?" Website&#039;s 1000 Greatest Films Poll.
